title: Erasure - Supernature (Dutch Treat ^B072 HQ Electronic Indie)
description:
Dedicated to my friend Jamal, who delivered 8 of the nine hours of interesting Erasure tracks. That is a lot even for the biggest fan. So now I tried to put it all in some very interesting 97 minutes of electronic and symphonic pop music (with a small tendency to overdo things :)). If you like Pet Shop Boys, Eurythmics, Ten Sharp, well then you know..... Enjoy,
